      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>What's New in 1.7.2</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Lock Screen: baked weather-effects video for static wallpapers with rain/snow (desktop keeps live Metal FX)</li>
          <li>Centralized wallpaper playback state (<code>WallpaperPlaybackState</code>, <code>WallpaperApplyService</code>)</li>
          <li>Fixed static+weather versioning save/select/restore</li>
          <li>Fixed Metal offline renderer crash (compute/render encoder ordering)</li>
          <li>Fixed SwiftFormat build phase scoping (was scanning entire repo including SPM checkouts)</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
